PrecisGranting of an annuity to VINCENT JOURDAIN, son of the Hon. Claude Raymond Jourdain, a deceased Puisne Judge of the Superior Court for the District of Québec in the Province of Quebec, commencing on December 31, 1992, and continuing thenceforth for so long as he is a child within the meaning of the Judges Act.

precis:
Granting of an annuity to VINCENT JOURDAIN, son of the Hon. Claude Raymond
Jourdain, a deceased Puisne Judge of the Superior Court for the District of
Québec in the Province of Quebec, commencing on December 31, 1992, and
continuing thenceforth for so long as he is a child within the meaning of
